{"tid":408341,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"南韓決定恢復向北韓提供人道援助","createTime":"2017-09-21T06:50:51.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-22T01:42:48.000Z","uid":32938,"like":2,"dislike":31,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"8ec3fb0603cf09507b0cf793e8d356bcb612df24","tid":408341,"uid":32938,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-21T06:50:51.000Z","msg":"【Now新聞台】南韓政府決定恢復向北韓提供人道援助，總額八百萬美元，落實日期待定。<br />\n<br />\n北韓近期再度核試，又頻頻試射導彈，令朝鮮半島局勢轉趨緊張，但南韓政府決定分開處理對北韓政權的制裁和對北韓民眾的人道援助。<br />\n<br />\n統一部公布，將會透過聯合國世界糧食計劃署和聯合國兒童基金會，向北韓兒童及孕婦提供總值八百萬美元的營養食品和醫療藥物等；至於何時落實，要在綜合考慮兩韓關係等情況後再作決定。<br />\n<br />\n南韓對上一次透過國際組織援助北韓是在2015年12月，今次是總統文在寅上台後首次決定提供援助，分析認為落實時間未定，是由於北韓不斷發起核導挑釁，要顧慮到南韓國內輿論。"},{"pid":"ac0b7e3b0b9e279a031b2dde8c840f88bcbf2d6e","tid":408341,"uid":20815,"like":21,"dislike":0,"score":21,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-21T06:52:32.000Z","msg":"屌你老母 垃圾豬隊友<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n送錢俾敵人射導彈轟自己<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b00f39e824a26dacb547af795c4b00a62f51dc4b","tid":408341,"uid":102096,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-21T06:53:43.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f75a9da3fc8cd9704abde8e403f8187137b634c0","tid":408341,"uid":37735,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-21T06:53:49.000Z","msg":"左膠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b41a0003766a4ebc9a4b4f526f9ab4b0f9b60de3","tid":408341,"uid":62599,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-21T06:54:00.000Z","msg":"垃撚圾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2944e0fd86eb70b9de7648b01b5bfc9653742094","tid":408341,"uid":45213,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-21T06:55:07.000Z","msg":"肥仔:好波!今晚射多幾枝導彈賀賀佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/